 A) puts coordinates directly on the `<text x=\"...\" y=\"...\">` element. These coordinates need to be in SVG coordinate space, not in container-relative space.\n\nSo the fix is: use SVG's getScreenCTM().inverse() to convert screen coordinates to SVG coordinates in handleCanvasClick, instead of the manual math.",
